<title>USA: Misonix says suit filed by Mentor Corp.</title>
<headline>Misonix says suit filed by Mentor Corp.</headline>
<dateline>FARMINGDALE, N.Y. 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Misonix Inc said on Thursday that its licensee, Medical Device Alliance Inc, had been sued for alleged patent infringement by Mentor Corp.</p>
<p>The suit also charged MDA's wholly owned subsidiary, LySonix Inc, Misonix said in a statement.</p>
<p>&quot;We believe that the suit filed by Mentor is without merit and substance,&quot; said LySonix president John Gimbel. He added that the company had retained counsel to pursue the case.</p>
<p>Misonix Inc develops and manufactures medical, scientific and industrial ultrasonic and air pollution control systems.</p>
<p>LySonix Inc markets the LySonix(TM) 2000 Ultrasonic Surgical System.</p>
